column5: What is the best way to get the remote canadian lake fall walleye? Cranking baits at night in that dark iron water? Also how late in the year do these fly-in resorts stay open? Mid october?
What is the best way to get the remote canadian lake fall walleye? Cranking baits at night in that dark iron water? Also how late in the year do these fly-in resorts stay open? Mid october?

My best quess would be to call some of the resorts. A good many of them are probably open due to the fact that they run moose camps out off them. I usually fish up until moose hunting starts which is Oct 5 this year.
